'''Kacbada''' '''[[Kacbo]]''' '''[[Bayt al-Xaraam]]''' ([[ingiriis]]: Kaaba; [[carabi]]: بيت الحرام; af-[[Soomaali]]: Kacbada<ref>"'''[[Kacbo]]''' '''[[Bayt al-Xaraam]]''' ([[ingiriis]]: Kaaba; [[carabi]]: بيت الحرام; af-[[Soomaali]]: Kacbada"</ref>) waa dhismo afar-gees ah (cuboid) oo  ku yaala magaalada [[Makka]] ee wadanka [[Sacuudi Carabiya]]. Waa dhismaha ugu muhiisan ee ugu barakeeysan isla markaana xudunta u ah [[diin]]ta [[Islaam]]ka.<ref>"[[Xajka]] [[12|12ka Dul-Xijah]]; [[15|15 milyan]] oo dad ah sanad kasta"</ref> 

[[Masaajid|Masaajidka al-Xaraam]] oo ah masaajidka ugu barkeeysan dhamaan masaajiida Islaamka waxaa laga dhisey agagaarka Kacbada. 
Kacbadu waa jihada loo soo tukado dhamaan [[salaad]]aha ay tukadaan [[dad]]ka [[muslim]]iinta ay meel kasta ooy dunida ka joogaan, taasi waxaa loo yaqaanaa '''[[Qiblo]]'''.
Mid ka mid ah [[shan|shanta tiir]] ee Islaamka ayaa wuxuu farayaa qof kasta oo muslim ah in uu soo siyaarto Kacbada barakeeysan, ugu yaraan, hal mar oo ka mid ah noloshiisa waa haddii uu awoodo dhaqaalaha iyo kharashka safarkaasi.

Noocyada kala duwan ee [[Xajka]] ayaa waxa ka mid ah '''Dawaafka''' oo ah in lagu wareego Kacbada [[7|7 jeer]]. Sidoo kale, wakhtiga '''Cumrada''' ayaa ayadna 7 jeer lagu wareegaa dhismaha Kacbada ee barakeysan. 
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, kacbadu waa masaajid aad u mashquul ah sababtoo ah dad badan oo muslimiin ah ayaa dhex jooga goor kasta. [[Wakhti]]ga ugu mashquulka badan Kacbada waa goorta ay dadka muslimiinta ahi ku gudo jiraan gudashada [[Xajka]] taasi oo ku beegan [[12|12ka Dul-Xija]] ee [[sanad]]ka Islaamka ama "Hijriga". Sanadkii [[2013]]ka dadka muslimiinta ah ee soo siyaartey Kacbada iyo dalka Sacuudi Carabiya waxaa maamulka Xajku ku sheegay 5,100,544 ([[5|5 milyan]]) oo qof.
 
Guud ahaan, kacbada oo ku dhex taala caasimada Makko waa hooyga uu u dhashay [[Nebi Muxamed]] (c.s.w),<ref>"Makko waa hooyga uu u dhashay [[Nebi Muxamed]] (c.s.w)"</ref> deegaankii ugu horeeyay ee lagu soo dejiyo waxyiga [[Qur'aan]]ka<ref>"lagu soo dejiyo waxyiga [[Qur'aan]]ka kariimka ah"</ref> kariimka ah, magaalada xudunta u ah [[diin]]ta [[Islaam]]ka, iyo meesha meesha uu ku yaalo [[masaajid|masaajidka barakaysan]] ee Kacbada taasi oo ah jihada loo tukado dhamaan [[Salaad]]aha.<ref>"xudunta u ah [[diin]]ta [[Islaam]]ka, iyo meesha meesha uu ku yaalo [[masaajid|masaajidka barakaysan]] ee [[Kacbada]]"</ref> 

Kacbada iyo guud ahaan caasimada [[Makkah]] waxaa wakhti aad u dheer maamulaayay [[qaraabo|qaraabada]] iyo [[qoys]]ka [[Nebi Muxamed]] (n.n.k.h) ee loo yaqaano "Shariifis"ka.<ref>"[[qaraabo|qaraabada]] iyo [[qoys]]ka [[Nebi Muxamed]] (n.n.k.h) ee loo yaqaano "Shariifis"ka"</ref> Laakiin markeey [[taariikh]]du ahayd [[sanad|sanadkii 1925tii]] dowlada boqortooyada wadanka [[Sacuudi Carabiya]] ayaa la wareegtay maamulka iyo gacan ku heeynta magaalada Makko, kuwaasi oo ilaa hada haya hogaanka iyo tallada caasimadan. Maamulka boqortooyada Sacuudigu aad ayuu u dhisay magaaladan, wuxuuna balaadhiyay dhismaha iyo baaxada ay ku fadhido Makko. Dhismayaasha wakhtigan lagu daray magaalada waxaa ka mid ah Abraj al Beyt oo ah [[3|dhismaha 3aad]] ee ugu dheer [[duni]]da iyo kan ugu weyn baaxada fadhi ee dunida.<ref>"Abraj al Beyt oo ah [[3|dhismaha 3aad]] ee ugu dheer [[duni]]da iyo kan ugu weyn baaxada fadhi ee dunida"</ref> 

Isku soo duuboo, magaalada barakeysan ee Makkah waxaa iskugu yimaada dad ka badan [[milyan|15 milyan]] oo muslimiin ah wakhtiyada kala duwan ee sanadka, taasi oo ka dhigtay caasimadan mida ugu isa-socodka badan dunida. Intaasi waxaa dheer magaalada Makkah looma ogola ineey tagaan ama dhex galaan dad aan muslim ahayn.<ref>''The Center of Islam'', Ahmed Husein, '''History of Islamic Empire:From the beginning to the present day''', Vol. IV, ed. M.A. Al-Bakhit, L. Bazin and A.Husein, (Islamic Study, 2008), 1190.[http://books.google.com/books?id=PvlthkbFU1UC&pg=PA1190&dq=islam+uqba+nafi&hl=en&sa=X&ei=C1A_UpKnLuv94AO_x4GgBQ&ved=0CEIQ6AEwBA#v=onepage&q=niger%20uqba%20nafi&f=false]</ref> 

